822
00:47:30,235 --> 00:47:32,244
It would've been better if I were ten years younger.

823
00:47:32,505 --> 00:47:34,675
If I didn't have Woo Ri back then...

824
00:47:39,215 --> 00:47:40,414
Two million dollars?

825
00:47:41,855 --> 00:47:43,114
You want her to carry out the pregnancy?

826
00:47:44,684 --> 00:47:45,824
Two million dollars?

827
00:47:48,324 --> 00:47:50,295
The answer is no even if you offer 20 million dollars.

828
00:47:50,625 --> 00:47:51,764
Why?

829
00:47:51,925 --> 00:47:53,324
Woo Ri is my daughter.

830
00:47:54,735 --> 00:47:56,434
You think money can solve everything, right?

831
00:47:57,465 --> 00:47:58,965
There are things you can't do with money.

832
00:47:59,505 --> 00:48:00,775
Not my daughter.

833
00:48:00,905 --> 00:48:02,235
You can't ruin her life...

834
00:48:03,534 --> 00:48:04,804
even if it can save my life.

835
00:48:09,974 --> 00:48:11,614
Ma'am. Why are you so unreasonable?

836
00:48:12,244 --> 00:48:13,585
Will she die from it?

837
00:48:13,855 --> 00:48:16,255
We're simply asking her to have the baby.

838
00:48:16,614 --> 00:48:18,723
Should we kill the baby in her womb?

839
00:48:18,724 --> 00:48:19,824
Will you commit murder?

840
00:48:20,054 --> 00:48:21,494
Hey! Watch your mouth!

841
00:48:22,324 --> 00:48:24,025
If you bring up money again,

842
00:48:24,425 --> 00:48:26,124
I'll arrest you all for violating Clause 3 of Article 23...

843
00:48:26,125 --> 00:48:28,634
of the Enforcement Rule of Bioethics and Safety Act.

844
00:48:28,635 --> 00:48:30,464
Who are you? A lawyer?

845
00:48:30,465 --> 00:48:31,534
When did you get here?

846
00:48:35,335 --> 00:48:36,675
What are you doing?

847
00:48:37,144 --> 00:48:39,045
Why are you meeting with them?

848
00:48:40,644 --> 00:48:42,414
