993
00:59:00,565 --> 00:59:01,934
I was wondering what happened.

994
00:59:02,335 --> 00:59:04,195
If there's a problem, I'll help too.

995
00:59:04,534 --> 00:59:06,105
There's no problem.

996
00:59:06,704 --> 00:59:10,275
Actually, there was something I need to tell you in person.

997
00:59:11,875 --> 00:59:14,573
Are you free tomorrow morning?

998
00:59:14,574 --> 00:59:16,144
I'll go to your hospital.

999
00:59:16,445 --> 00:59:20,414
Sure. But what's this about?

1000
00:59:21,284 --> 00:59:23,614
I'll tell you in person.

1001
00:59:36,394 --> 00:59:37,593
You're certain, right?

1002
00:59:37,594 --> 00:59:39,405
Yes!

1003
00:59:39,605 --> 00:59:41,203
She said she would have the baby.

1004
00:59:41,204 --> 00:59:42,774
I had a feeling she would...

1005
00:59:42,775 --> 00:59:44,604
when she left without getting the procedure.

1006
00:59:44,605 --> 00:59:47,105
There's always a way out!

1007
00:59:47,304 --> 00:59:49,574
You were right about everything.

1008
00:59:49,644 --> 00:59:51,784
- We must be positive. - We must be positive.

1009
01:00:03,155 --> 01:00:04,525
It was perfect until now.

1010
01:00:05,494 --> 01:00:07,224
I forgot about this problem.

1011
01:00:08,695 --> 01:00:11,064
Mom. What do I do?

1012
01:00:11,065 --> 01:00:14,704
