1013
01:00:15,735 --> 01:00:17,335
Gosh. There's a bug!

1014
01:00:35,894 --> 01:00:37,155
Hey, you're here.

1015
01:00:37,795 --> 01:00:41,094
If that couple is the parent, the baby will be happy for sure.

1016
01:00:41,735 --> 01:00:45,163
But we should discuss this thoroughly with the couple.

1017
01:00:45,164 --> 01:00:47,104
It won't be as easy as you might think.

1018
01:00:47,105 --> 01:00:48,835
We'll have to draw up legal documents too.

1019
01:00:49,335 --> 01:00:50,905
So...

1020
01:00:51,405 --> 01:00:54,105
we should talk to them first.

1021
01:00:54,815 --> 01:00:57,074
If you don't agree with them, you can change your mind.

1022
01:00:58,644 --> 01:01:00,445
- Kang Jae. - Yes?

1023
01:01:01,255 --> 01:01:03,715
I'm so relieved to have you by my side.

1024
01:01:15,195 --> 01:01:16,534
Hello.

1025
01:01:17,094 --> 01:01:19,704
Thank you for coming to our hospital.

1026
01:01:26,005 --> 01:01:27,105
No Man Chul.

1027
01:01:33,485 --> 01:01:34,585
No Man Chul!

